*ffmpegsource-2.17 (12 Feb 2012)

  12 Feb 2012; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org> +ffmpegsource-2.17.ebuild,
  ffmpegsource-9999.ebuild:
  Bump to 2.17, remove postproc use flag from 9999. Bug 403265. Thanks to Nikoli

  23 Dec 2011; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org> ffmpegsource-9999.ebuild:
  Fix dep in 9999 too

  17 Dec 2011; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  ffmpegsource-2.16.2.1_pre587.ebuild:
  works fine with ffmpeg 0.9, updating dep

  10 Dec 2011; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org>
  ffmpegsource-2.16.2.1_pre587.ebuild:
  Change virtual/ffmpeg depend to >=media-video/libav-0.8_pre20111116 as
  ffmpegsource doesn't compile with older libav or any ffmpeg. Bug 393313

